102
00:09:51,980 --> 00:09:53,730
<font size="20"><b>No exorcism.</b></font>

103
00:09:54,610 --> 00:09:56,900
<font size="20"><b>I'll have Evil Eye join my family.</b></font>

104
00:09:58,280 --> 00:10:00,120
<font size="20"><b>Huh? What? What did you just say?</b></font>

105
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:05,960
<font size="20"><b>Sorry to do this after coming
