106
00:10:07,210 --> 00:10:10,170
<font size="20"><b>Oh, I see. I understand.</b></font>

107
00:10:13,130 --> 00:10:14,880
<font size="20"><b>You sure, Grandma?</b></font>

108
00:10:14,880 --> 00:10:18,260
<font size="20"><b>You heard Jiji.
Can't do anything about it.</b></font>

109
00:10:18,550 --> 00:10:22,930
<font size="20"><b>I personally like that kind of spirit in Jiji.</b></font>

110
00:10:24,060 --> 00:10:28,140
<font size="20"><b>Then, what? We have to keep
taking care of this guy forever?</b></font>

111
00:10:28,140 --> 00:10:30,150
<font size="20"><b>I totally don't want to!</b></font>

112
00:10:30,650 --> 00:10:35,150
<font size="20"><b>I don't want my precious time
to be wasted because of his selfishness!</b></font>

113
00:10:38,650 --> 00:10:42,620
<font size="20"><b>Then, I'll learn how to hold Evil Eye back.</b></font>

114
00:10:44,030 --> 00:10:48,000
