even if he were to transform, right?</b></font>

116
00:10:51,130 --> 00:10:54,500
<font size="20"><b>But is that something you need to go
out of your way to do, Takakura?</b></font>

117
00:10:54,880 --> 00:10:56,960
<font size="20"><b>You won't be able to sleep
peacefully anymore!</b></font>

118
00:10:57,170 --> 00:10:58,970
<font size="20"><b>Your life will be in danger.</b></font>

119
00:11:00,890 --> 00:11:02,220
<font size="20"><b>He's my friend.</b></font>

120
00:11:07,640 --> 00:11:09,520
<font size="20"><b>Then I'll become stronger, too.</b></font>

121
00:11:09,520 --> 00:11:11,270
<font size="20"><b>It's easier if there's two of us, right?</b></font>

122
00:11:11,270 --> 00:11:12,520
<font size="20"><b>Hold on!</b></font>

123
00:11:12,520 --> 00:11:16,230
