124
00:11:16,230 --> 00:11:18,070
<font size="20"><b>I'd like to see you try, you ugly hag!</b></font>

125
00:11:18,400 --> 00:11:21,530
<font size="20"><b>Okarun, let me hug you.</b></font>

126
00:11:24,490 --> 00:11:26,490
<font size="20"><b>Okarun!</b></font>

127
00:11:27,580 --> 00:11:28,450
<font size="20"><b>You guys!</b></font>

128
