131
00:11:46,810 --> 00:11:49,930
<font size="20"><b>{\an8}TOSHIRO</b></font>

132
00:11:50,230 --> 00:11:52,310
<font size="20"><b>Yeah. Great work.</b></font>

133
00:11:55,730 --> 00:11:58,570
<font size="20"><b>We might call you again real soon.</b></font>

134
