136
00:12:19,460 --> 00:12:21,550
<font size="20"><b>Sit on your legs, back straight.</b></font>

137
00:12:22,260 --> 00:12:24,180
<font size="20"><b>Clench up your lower abs.</b></font>

138
00:12:24,470 --> 00:12:29,310
<font size="20"><b>Imagine a laser beam coming out of the top
