139
00:12:33,940 --> 00:12:35,940
<font size="20"><b>Don't fall over even when you get pushed.</b></font>

140
00:12:35,940 --> 00:12:38,480
<font size="20"><b>Sit like you're rooted to the ground.</b></font>

141
00:12:38,480 --> 00:12:39,780
<font size="20"><b>Sure.</b></font>

142
00:12:39,780 --> 00:12:44,110
<font size="20"><b>Jiji, like this.
