143
00:12:44,860 --> 00:12:46,450
<font size="20"><b>Try pushing really hard.</b></font>

144
00:12:46,450 --> 00:12:48,030
<font size="20"><b>Huh? Really?</b></font>

145
00:12:51,080 --> 00:12:54,080
