176
00:16:53,490 --> 00:16:56,620
<font size="20"><b>I thought I wanted
to say things like that, too.</b></font>

177
00:16:57,410 --> 00:17:00,870
<font size="20"><b>In my case, I'm just acting tough.</b></font>

178
00:17:01,620 --> 00:17:06,000
<font size="20"><b>But I want to look cool, even if
