203
00:18:57,950 --> 00:19:06,200
<font size="20"><b>{\an8}Motivation! Courage! Spirit! Sincerity!
Huh? What was it? Sincerity! Tenacity!</b></font>

204
00:18:58,530 --> 00:18:59,700
