210
00:19:16,300 --> 00:19:17,380
<font size="20"><b>What's gotten into you?</b></font>

211
00:19:17,380 --> 00:19:18,760
<font size="20"><b>I'm going to rebuild the house!</b></font>

212
00:19:18,760 --> 00:19:19,680
<font size="20"><b>Wicked!</b></font>

213
00:19:19,680 --> 00:19:21,720
<font size="20"><b>- What about your smartphone?
- Like I need something like that.</b></font>

214
00:19:23,140 --> 00:19:26,060
<font size="20"><b>Right now, we're seeking warmth.</b></font>

215
00:19:26,060 --> 00:19:28,230
<font size="20"><b>Was your house that cold?</b></font>

216
00:19:28,230 --> 00:19:30,270
<font size="20"><b>I mean, it's frigid, of course!</b></font>

217
00:19:30,270 --> 00:19:33,520
<font size="20"><b>Wasn't Ririna saying that she was looking
