218
00:19:37,820 --> 00:19:40,200
<font size="20"><b>Oh, she was. Was it for a restaurant?</b></font>

219
00:19:40,320 --> 00:19:42,910
<font size="20"><b>Seriously? Tell her I'll totally do it!</b></font>

220
00:19:42,910 --> 00:19:45,490
<font size="20"><b>But Momo, you never last long
