225
00:19:54,170 --> 00:19:57,420
<font size="20"><b>It's fine! I have grown up!</b></font>

226
00:19:57,420 --> 00:20:00,420
<font size="20"><b>I won't give up oh so easily!</b></font>

227
00:20:00,630 --> 00:20:02,800
<font size="20"><b>Did you hear that, Ms. Muko?</b></font>

228
00:20:02,800 --> 00:20:04,680
<font size="20"><b>I did hear it, Ms. Mi.</b></font>

229
00:20:08,140 --> 00:20:10,020
<font size="20"><b>Okarun!</b></font>

230
00:20:13,350 --> 00:20:16,900
<font size="20"><b>Momo said she got a part-time job today,
so you can go home without her.</b></font>

231
00:20:17,480 --> 00:20:20,150
<font size="20"><b>All right. I understand.</b></font>

232
00:20:20,780 --> 00:20:22,740
<font size="20"><b>- And...
- ...so!</b></font>

233
00:20:23,360 --> 00:20:25,240
<font size="20"><b>You should go on a date with us!</b></font>

234
00:20:25,530 --> 00:20:27,280
<font size="20"><b>What? I decline!</b></font>

235
00:20:27,450 --> 00:20:28,660
<font size="20"><b>Come with us, you punk!</b></font>

236
00:20:28,660 --> 00:20:30,500
<font size="20"><b>Don't resist!</b></font>

237
00:20:34,250 --> 00:20:35,750
<font size="20"><b>Hold on, wait!</b></font>

238
00:20:35,880 --> 00:20:37,710
<font size="20"><b>I'm not gonna go on a date!</b></font>

239
00:20:37,710 --> 00:20:39,380
<font size="20"><b>We're just gonna have some tea!</b></font>

240
00:20:39,380 --> 00:20:41,970
<font size="20"><b>Don't you call that a date?</b></font>

241
00:20:42,800 --> 00:20:45,760
<font size="20"><b>Then if Momo and Jiji were having tea,
would that be a date?</b></font>

242
00:20:45,760 --> 00:20:46,680
<font size="20"><b>Of course not.</b></font>

243
00:20:46,800 --> 00:20:49,680
<font size="20"><b>Then tell us what's so different
when it's us, damn it!</b></font>

244
00:20:51,350 --> 00:20:53,060
<font size="20"><b>No way!</b></font>

245
00:21:18,960 --> 00:21:20,050
