246
00:21:25,050 --> 00:21:27,550
<font size="20"><b>I really don't want to!</b></font>

247
00:21:28,300 --> 00:21:29,930
<font size="20"><b>Okarun, this way! Over here!</b></font>

248
00:21:30,220 --> 00:21:32,930
<font size="20"><b>I'm not going to drink one drop of tea!</b></font>

249
00:21:33,180 --> 00:21:34,310
<font size="20"><b>You'll get thirsty.</b></font>

250
00:21:34,310 --> 00:21:35,560
<font size="20"><b>No, I won't!</b></font>

251
00:21:35,690 --> 00:21:38,310
<font size="20"><b>Absolutely sure?
