252
00:21:38,480 --> 00:21:40,150
<font size="20"><b>I won't drink!</b></font>

253
00:21:41,730 --> 00:21:44,240
<font size="20"><b>Welcome home, master!</b></font>

254
00:21:51,040 --> 00:21:52,500
<font size="20"><b>How many in your party?</b></font>

255
00:21:52,500 --> 00:21:54,790
<font size="20"><b>Three!</b></font>

256
00:21:58,040 --> 00:22:01,130
<font size="20"><b>Hey, you maid over there!
Make sure to serve us well.</b></font>

257
00:22:01,590 --> 00:22:03,300
<font size="20"><b>Wait, Okarun?</b></font>

258
00:22:03,550 --> 00:22:04,970
<font size="20"><b>M-Miss Ayase!</b></font>

259
00:22:13,810 --> 00:22:15,390
<font size="20"><b>Come on now.</b></font>

260
00:22:19,230 --> 00:22:21,770
<font size="20"><b>Welcome home, master!</b></font>

261
00:23:52,950 --> 00:23:55,660
