262
00:23:55,660 --> 00:23:57,620
<font size="20"><b>Everything's expensive, you idiot!</b></font>

263
00:23:57,620 --> 00:23:59,710
<font size="20"><b>A house with no food? I'll just run away!</b></font>

264
00:23:59,710 --> 00:24:00,750
<font size="20"><b>Fine, then, leave!</b></font>

265
